    <div class="qb-sub-faq-item">
      <div class="qb-sub-faq-q">
        What time will my order be delivered?
        <svg class="qb-sub-faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="qb-sub-faq-a">Daily subscriptions are delivered between 6 AM – 8 AM. Weekly subscriptions arrive on your chosen day before noon. You can set your preferred time in your account settings.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="qb-sub-faq-item">
      <div class="qb-sub-faq-q">
        How does the discount work?
        <svg class="qb-sub-faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="qb-sub-faq-a">Subscription prices are already discounted from the regular per-item price. You save between 8–20% automatically. No coupon needed.</div>
